<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Travel Buddy Finder</title>
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/about.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-container">
          <a href="/" class="logo">
            <i class='bx bx-trip'></i>
            <span>TravelBuddy</span>
          </a>
      
          <div class="search-container" style="background-color: inherit;">
            <!-- Search moved to filter section -->
          </div>
      
          <nav>
            <ul>
              <a href="/">Home</a>
              <li><a href="/destinations">Destinations</a></li>
              <li><a href="/find-buddy">Find a Buddy</a></li>
              <li><a href="/about-us">About Us</a></li>
              <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
              <li><a href="/dashboard" class="nav-item-with-badge">
        Dashboard
        <% if (locals.user && locals.incomingRequests && incomingRequests.length > 0) { %>
          <span class="notification-badge"><%= incomingRequests.length %></span>
        <% } %>
      </a>
</li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
          <form action="/auth/logout" method="POST" style="display: inline;">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline">Logout</button>
          </form>          
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>About Travel Buddy Finder</h1>
                <p>India's premier platform for connecting travelers</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <img src="/api/placeholder/500/300" alt="People traveling in India">
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <p>Travel Buddy Finder was born from a simple idea: exploring India is better when shared with the right companion. Founded in 2023, we've been on a mission to connect like-minded travelers and foster meaningful connections throughout the diverse landscapes of India.</p>
                        <p>What started as a small community of adventure seekers in Mumbai has grown into a nationwide network of travelers helping each other discover the incredible beauty and culture that India has to offer.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mission-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="mission-content">
                    <div class="mission-icon">
                        <i class='bx bx-target-lock'></i>
                    </div>
                    <p>To create a safe, inclusive platform where Indian travelers can find compatible companions, share experiences, and make the most of their journeys across our beautiful country.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="values-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
                <div class="values-grid">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <i class='bx bx-shield-quarter'></i>
                        <h3>Safety First</h3>
                        <p>We verify profiles and provide tools for secure communication between members across India.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <i class='bx bx-group'></i>
                        <h3>Community</h3>
                        <p>We foster a supportive community of Indian travelers who help each other explore and grow.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <i class='bx bx-world'></i>
                        <h3>Inclusivity</h3>
                        <p>We welcome travelers from all backgrounds, cultures, and regions of India.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <i class='bx bx-bulb'></i>
                        <h3>Innovation</h3>
                        <p>We constantly improve our platform to better serve our Indian community's needs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="india-focus-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Exploring India Together</h2>
                <div class="india-content">
                    <p>India is a vast country with incredible diversity - from the snow-capped Himalayas to the tropical beaches of Kerala, from the deserts of Rajasthan to the lush greenery of the Northeast. With such variety, finding the right travel companion who shares your interests and travel style can transform your journey.</p>
                    <div class="region-grid">
                        <div class="region-card">
                            <i class='bx bx-landscape'></i>
                            <h3>North India</h3>
                            <p>Find buddies for Himalayan treks, spiritual journeys, and cultural explorations</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-card">
                            <i class='bx bx-water'></i>
                            <h3>South India</h3>
                            <p>Connect with travelers interested in beaches, temples, and backwater adventures</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-card">
                            <i class='bx bx-building-house'></i>
                            <h3>West India</h3>
                            <p>Meet companions for desert safaris, heritage sites, and metropolitan experiences</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-card">
                            <i class='bx bx-tree'></i>
                            <h3>East & Northeast</h3>
                            <p>Find partners for exploring tea gardens, tribal cultures, and untouched landscapes</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="team-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
                <div class="team-grid">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <div class="member-image">
                            <img src="/api/placeholder/250/250" alt="Team member">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Vikram Sharma</h3>
                        <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                        <div class="social-icons">
                            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-linkedin'></i></a>
                            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-twitter'></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <div class="member-image">
                            <img src="/api/placeholder/250/250" alt="Team member">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Priya Patel</h3>
                        <p>Head of Product</p>
                        <div class="social-icons">
                            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-linkedin'></i></a>
                            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-twitter'></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <div class="member-image">
                            <img src="/api/placeholder/250/250" alt="Team member">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Arjun Mehta</h3>
                        <p>Community Manager</p>
                        <div class="social-icons">
                            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-linkedin'></i></a>
                            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-twitter'></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="stats-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <i class='bx bx-user-check'></i>
                        <span class="counter" data-target="25000">0</span>
                        <p>Happy Users</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <i class='bx bx-map-alt'></i>
                        <span class="counter" data-target="28">0</span>
                        <p>States & UTs Covered</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <i class='bx bx-calendar-check'></i>
                        <span class="counter" data-target="5000">0</span>
                        <p>Trips Organized</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <i class='bx bx-happy-heart-eyes'></i>
                        <span class="counter" data-target="98">0</span>
                        <p>% Satisfaction</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="testimonials-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
                <div class="testimonials-slider">
                    <div class="testimonial active">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <i class='bx bxs-quote-alt-left quote-icon'></i>
                            <p>"Travel Buddy Finder helped me find the perfect companion for my trip to Ladakh. We've now been friends for over a year and have traveled to 5 different states together!"</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <h4>Meera S.</h4>
                                <p>Delhi, India</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <i class='bx bxs-quote-alt-left quote-icon'></i>
                            <p>"As a solo female traveler, safety was my biggest concern. This platform gave me the confidence to find trustworthy travel partners and explore the hidden gems of Northeast India."</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <h4>Priya K.</h4>
                                <p>Mumbai, India</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <i class='bx bxs-quote-alt-left quote-icon'></i>
                            <p>"I was looking for someone to share travel expenses during my Kerala trip, but I found something much more valuable - a genuine friendship that made my journey through God's Own Country unforgettable."</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <h4>Rohan B.</h4>
                                <p>Bangalore, India</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-controls">
                    <button class="prev-btn"><i class='bx bx-chevron-left'></i></button>
                    <div class="dots">
                        <span class="dot active" data-index="0"></span>
                        <span class="dot" data-index="1"></span>
                        <span class="dot" data-index="2"></span>
                    </div>
                    <button class="next-btn"><i class='bx bx-chevron-right'></i></button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Find Your Travel Buddy?</h2>
                <p>Join thousands of Indian travelers and start planning your next adventure with the perfect companion.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up Now</a>
                    <a href="/support" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn How It Works</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
